Description:

*** Ready to Ship - Set of 3 cast iron bottle openers.  ***
These cast iron bottle openers can be used to mount on a piece of wood or your porch railing.  The openers can be hand painted and distressed to give them a unique look.  These make great groomsman gifts, and you can paint them to match your wedding colors.  You can include a bottle opener on many woodworking projects, including beer caddies or tool boxes.  
This listing is for a set of 3 rustic bottle openers, in the rustic brown finish shown.  Each bottle opener is about 3" high and 2.75" wide.  Bottle openers are in a rustic brown finish (as shown in first 4 photos) and say 'Open Here' across the top. 
Screws are optional - select either with or without screws when purchasing.  If purchased with screws, six 1" black screws will be included.
